# NIX EDIT
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Open the Nix expression of a package in your editor.
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix edit nixpkgs#hello: Open the derivation of 'hello' in $EDITOR.

### Essentials
- nix edit .#my-package: Open a package defined in the local flake.

## Tips
- Extremely useful for understanding how a package is built or for debugging build issues.

## Disclaimers
- Requires the $EDITOR environment variable to be set.

